caption: Best meal of the year.  Best way I can explain it is "Fresh"!

This place is serving up some of the best food in Lafayette right now with the freshest local ingredients.  The burger is a must try.  The Breakfast Burrito is epic and can easily be shared by two.  And last but not least, the Boudini is my goto for breakfast...so amazing!
Farm to table fresh every day! We love y'all.
This place is straight fire
I tried the hamburger. It was one of the best burgers I've ever tasted!!
Nice atmosphere, staff very friendly! Excellent Vegan burger and tasty Vegan blueberry pie!!

Such good wholesome food located here in Lafayette!  I could not believe it myself!  Service is always awesome and food is always great!  Everything here is pretty much good, but their breakfast burritos are slap your mama good, yes, that good!  Do yourself a favor and get one when you can!!!

Very, very satisfied with this place and the meal. Atmosphere is welcoming. Staff is pleasant and friendly. The food didn't seem like it would be my type at first. But after digging into the menu, I found a burger that was divine. Beet ketchup is awesome. And that lavender lemonade is mind blowing. Overall, a great experience.
Try the Lavender Lemonade - it’s refreshing iridescent purple deliciousness.

Adorable little spot. It was hard to choose what to order because it all sounded so delicious. They were out of a few of the protein options but gave great recommendations about what would be a good substitute. It's a bit loud in there but is great for a causal meal. They had several outside tables but we opted to wait and sit indoors.

First time here~loved everything about this place. I got the bagel sandwich and it was perfect. So flavorful and I loved the mustard it came with. Also, the presentation of the plate was so pretty to look at. You can tell so much care and love went into this craft. I will definitely make a point to eat here whenever I am in lafayette.
Loved It. Awesome food, service and feel.

Our first time visiting the restaurant(have eaten at her food truck),decor and food were both fantastic.  I had the seasonal salad and my husband had the scratch plate,both exceptional. We ate outside,street was quiet and lots of outdoor seating.

Lafayette's best kept secret! Amazing locally sourced seasonal menu that impresses me every time I visit.  It's spotlessly clean and tastefully decorated. I love the focus on a sustainable serving experience. The dessert box always has hidden treasures.

Love their ambience, and their farm to kitchen food concept!  Food is always fresh and tasty!  The service is superb!  Just hate that they do not open long enough so I can enjoy their food throughout the day!  MUST VISIT and try everything!  EDIT: Such good wholesome food located here in Lafayette!  I could not believe it myself!  Service is always awesome and food is always great!  Everything here is pretty much good, but their breakfast burritos are slap your mama good, yes, that good!  Do yourself a favor and get one when you can!!!
Vegan options available...😋
Delicious food, amazing atmosphere, and wonderful customer service!
PERFECT and vegan friendly! Best place in Lafayette IMO. Do yourself a favor and get the hot Chai tea👌
Cute little spot with healthy delicious burgers. Was nice to have something different! Try the burger!!
So fresh and delicious! Large portions each entree can easily be shared.
The food is spectacular!
This was some of the best food I've ever put in my mouth. The lavender lemonade is absolutely to die for. I wish I could bathe in it.

Food was very good, original and creative, but the experience was diminished by the person taking our order wearing her mask below her mouth while we were in close proximity (despite signs everywhere). All the rest of the staff and customers were properly masked. Won’t be returning, at least until the pandemic ends.
Always amazed!
Excellent food and service! 1 L🧡ve

A WONDERFUL place to eat. I was absolutely blown away when I walked in and then blown away a second time when I ate the food I ordered. Striking modern farmhouse atmosphere and fresh high quality food that actually tastes amazing.  I had a burger and a lavender lemonade and it was to die for. For picky eaters, don't shy away from this place. Even the less common ingredients on here are cooked or pickled or seasoned to perfection. It was a little intimidating at first but I cannot stress enough how incredibly worth it trying it was.
Fantastic fresh food and wines, get the scratch breakfast if possible, but everything is fantastic, friendly staff and ample area to dine outdoors

The food was amazing! My husband is very sceptable about restaurants with " health food " tasting good, he is a meat and potatoes kinda person. He was very pleased with the salad he got that had chicken on it. He bragged about the taste and that he felt full and stayed that way until dinner time. All of the staff was very friendly!
Great service,awesome food!
Pretty plate pork taste as good as it looks, in fact the whole place surprised me good. Live in Baton Rouge but it would be worth the drive to come eat here.
This place is awesome beyond compare.  Fresh, exciting eats that no other restaurant in Lafayette can be compared to.  Lady’s, y’all are outstanding 🤙🏽🤙🏽

Sometimes you can count on food transcending the descriptor "good" by being so dependable and so invested with care that it cannot abide by mundane terminology. Scratch comes so close to being Lafayette's neighborhood kitchen not by foisting some Tony Cachere soaked false narrative or even by executing culinary wizardry but by taking care with every aspect of what they produce.
Delicious!!
This restaurant serves food that is not only appealing to the eye, but the soul as well. So delicious and always fresh! I have never had a dish that I did not like. Farm to table at it's finest!
What an amazing place. They have basically all scratch-made foods that are incredible flavor combinations. Well done!
Simply amazing.
It doesn’t get any better than Scratch Kitchen. Amazing local food prepared by awesome people.
Great food and atmosphere! The burgers are amazing!

Great food, unique, good laid back atmosphere.  The counter surrounding the kitchen is nice.  A little on the pricey side but everything is sourced locally so worth it.  Can’t go wrong with the ground beef burrito. I do wish they were open more often though.
The food is amazing, the staff is very welcoming, the chefs are brilliant, and the seating area is cozy.
Everything was done to perfection

Fresh. Quality. Delicious. Much love to this wonderful local gem. Wish I could eat here more often but as a school teacher it's never open when I'm available. So the few times I do get to enjoy I relish every moment.
Outstanding farm fresh hand-crafted food!
Man oh man, I can’t recommend it enough! great food and great service!! They had a food truck on campus I went to, and now they have a restaurant. I WILL FOLLOW THEM ANYWHERE.
it was hard to choose from your eclectic menu. But everything looked great & my food was delicious! I am completely addicted to your beets and that delicious lavender lemonade.
so good!!!
Super fresh and Excellent food, clean restaurant, great staff,

If you are looking for a fresh assortment of food for lunch, then you will absolutely love this place.  The atmosphere, the people, and the food are refreshing.  Stop by for veggie burgers, grass fed beef, or pork patties cooked with love.  Grab a side of freshly grilled vegetables, a kombucha, some tea, or freshly squeezed satsumas.  Everything is so fresh.  Enjoy the laid back kitchen with the owner at the grill.  I highly recommend this place for a change of pace from the heavy ingredients of most Louisiana food at a reasonable price.

Some of the best food in Lafayette hands down. Great tasting healthy food that you can feel good about eating, and they have options for everyone that are all very reasonably priced. Great to support a business with sustainable practices that care so much about what they're serving and how it affects the environment.
Fresh made daily, breakfast all day, sandwiches, wraps, soup and salads, vegetarian choices. Food was delicious and staff was friendly.
Best food in the area. Comfortable building and friendly staff. Highly recommended.
The place is clean, decor is comfortable casual. Staff is friendly and courteous.  Food was delicious and fresh.
best healthy restaurant in lafay. serving fresh herbs & veggies from local farms
Amazing vegan options.
Great food with a fun vibe. Very casual and friendly, with nice decor. They also run the Scratch Kitchen food truck that is so delicious!
Delicious.  Super fresh and wonderful ingredients. Really busy at lunch time.
Fresh and delicious!
Your mouth will thank you, and your stomach will be asking for more! Très bon!!

Food was delectable and fresh, atmosphere was neat, cashier friendly, unfortunately the server was unnecessarily rude. I wanted to like this place but it was a disappointing and uncomfortable experience.

The food truck was outstanding and the restaurant also exceeds expectations. Locally sourced and scratch made, like the name says. My lunch partner loved the breakfast biscuits served all day. I had a veggie burger. Everything top notch, from the quick-pickled cuke garnish to the tomato relish.

Delicious farm to table restaurant. So farm to table, in fact, that their herbs grow around their building and they've got chickens and more behind their restaurant. I got the comfort bowl with hash potatoes that was more than enough food. Servers were very friendly and the atmosphere was homey. The food is always fresh and delicious. They inspire my own home cooking!

Probably the best quality food in Lafayette. Everything is locally grown/harvested/sourced and you can definitely taste the difference. Today I got their "phat chicken" sandwich with cucumber salad as a side. The sandwich was prepared perfectly and was so filling that I almost could not finish the cucumber salad. Definitely worth stopping by and trying out. They are changing the game here.
local, sustainable, and highest quality food made by the best people. don't miss it this local favorite.
Amazing vegan burger! Thanks for opening a healthy restaurant option in Lafayette!
ABSOLUTELY DELICIOUS food, GREAT FRIENDLY OWNER & STAFF

Simple, fresh, seasonal and unexpected.  Great combinations of fresh veggies, fruit and perfectly cooked meats along with lots of vegetarian options too.  The eggplant burger or the breakfast burritos - both wonderful choices.  Great to see locals cranking out such wonderful food at a fair price in the “old” downtown Lafayette. Can’t wait til my next visit!!!
Great service,  atmosphere and food
I've loved their truck food at festivals, now I can sit down in the restaurant and enjoy.

The flexibility of Scratch is one of their calling cards, ever since before they began operating with a food-truck.  Just today I experienced the most satisfying all beef and herbed meatballs with zucchini and carrot noodles, parmesan, with a savory pot-liquor like sauce that melded the flavors together.  This has been one of the many palate surprises over the years. Also valued for many of us has been their sourcing of locally produced, raised, grown ingredients as much as feasible, coupled with that emphasis on growing the local food economy.  Lastly, not inconsequentially, since so many of us have to choose between time to linger over our lunch, and time sensitive commitments, I personally value their decision to serve takeaway orders in renewable, compostable packaging.  Near the coast, in this land of many rivers, what we do has an outsized impact on the health of the gulf's fisheries, and habitat for all the wonderful creatures of the sea that we don't fish for too.  As a familar voice counseled many of us, "Keep up the Good World."

Everything I've tried here has been unbelievably delicious and cooked perfectly. Everything is fresh and the menu changes based on what is available from the owners' farm. Do not pass up an opportunity to eat here. The absolute best breakfast and lunch you will find in Lafayette.
High quality food and service!
